				  					<li><a href="/plateforme-elsa/associations-membres-de-la-plateforme-elsa/"><img width="97" height="86" src="http://www.plateforme-elsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Logo_Solidarite.png" class="attachment-medium wp-post-image" alt="Logo_Solidarite" /></a></li>
				          
